OL,3,CFourteen train passengers treated
OL,4,Cafter 'smell of chemicals' reported
OL,6,FFourteen train passengers received
OL,7,Fmedical treatment after a smell of
OL,8,Fchemicals was reported on an
OL,9,Funderground platform at a major London
OL,10,Frailway station, firefighters said.
OL,12,FThe incident happened at Farringdon
OL,13,Fstation in the centre of the capital
OL,14,Fon Thursday morning.
OL,16,FThe station was evacuated and closed,
OL,17,Fbut has since reopened.
