OL,3,CFourteen train passengers treated
OL,4,Cafter 'smell of chemicals' reported
OL,6,FLFB said it was called about the
OL,7,Fincident at 9.41am and dispatched
OL,8,Fvarious units including two fire
OL,9,Fengines.
OL,11,FThe scene was declared safe by 11.35am.
OL,13,FBritish Transport Police (BTP) said it
OL,14,Fbelieved a "small number of people
OL,15,Fpotentially came into contact with an
OL,16,Funknown substance".
OL,18,FThe incident was initially treated as
OL,19,Fa suspected gas leak.
OL,26,@vD@LOUxD@RO]
