OL,3,CFourteen train passengers treated
OL,4,Cafter 'smell of chemicals' reported
OL,6,FBTP said armed police attended the
OL,7,Fscene as part of the response by the
OL,8,Femergency services, which is "typical
OL,9,Fduring a significant incident and
OL,10,Fshould not cause undue concern to the
OL,11,Fpublic in this case".
